Run these commands in order:

1. `dotnet build sdk/monitor/Azure.Provisioning.Monitor/`
2. `dotnet test sdk/monitor/Azure.Provisioning.Monitor/ --filter TestCategory!=Live`
3. `eng/scripts/Update-Snippets.ps1 monitor` — confirm README is updated correctly by checking git diff
4. `eng/scripts/Export-API.ps1 monitor` — only needed if public API surface was changed (not expected for doc-only changes)
5. `dotnet format sdk/monitor/Azure.Provisioning.Monitor/`

